title: The Genie from downunder. - Vol. 2.

brief_description: From the producers of “Round the twist” and “Skytrackers” the next two episodes in this series are: “Good cop, bad genie” and “Customs” and continue the adventures of Penelope Townes and the two genies Bruce and his son Baz.
